{"tid":1961561,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［新缸養魚］啲魚陸續死","createTime":"2020-04-07T01:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T10:26:44.000Z","uid":92052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"89e607ecb319c3618a8dbfff6796a8a8bf386035","tid":1961561,"uid":92052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:09:24.000Z","msg":"養咗一個月水左右<br />\n一開始幾條闖缸孔雀魚到而家都平安無事<br />\n以為養好菌，水質穩定啦<br />\n但最近一星期買嗰批孔雀魚開始逐漸瓜老襯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一日死一至兩條<br />\n有條死咗嗰身體直程有結晶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今早死嗰條腰部發黃<br />\n<br />\n唔知係因為本身批魚有病定關我缸水質事<br />\n<br />\n好驚全缸覆沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早幾天開始全缸落黃粉<br />\n希望其他魚挨得過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HqXE7wz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHqXE7wz.png&h=83b4d35a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QNCYDDA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQNCYDDA.png&h=605aba35&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc82fdc7d5a1d58c8a720fc994fc67db5849b06e","tid":1961561,"uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:11:41.000Z","msg":"屋企風水唔好養咩都死"},{"pid":"3017555d655c66b6bdcedc44e103dcea9985faa0","tid":1961561,"uid":4229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:16:00.000Z","msg":"影埋個景啦 二來袋裝魚好易有菌"},{"pid":"f723d2b03577f57eedab7834eb6fb4dce41286b6","tid":1961561,"uid":92052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc82fdc7d5a1d58c8a720fc994fc67db5849b06e","tid":1961561,"uid":58316,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:11:41.000Z","msg":"屋企風水唔好養咩都死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T01:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但屋企啲神獸越黎越生猛"},{"pid":"64e06a2e68f7820d8ba5b139b5f16d9f9f1ec044","tid":1961561,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco